    "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12",
    "summary": "Source text for Joshua 12 in Brenton's English Septuagint."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.1",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:1",
      "text": "And these are the kings of the land, whom the children of Israel slew, and inherited their land beyond Jordan from the east, from the valley of Arnon to the mount of Aermon, and all the land of Araba on the east.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.2",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:2",
      "text": "Seon king of the Amorites, who dwelt in Esebon, ruling from Arnon, which is in the valley, on the side of the valley, and half of Galaad as far as Jaboc, the borders of the children of Ammon.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.3",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:3",
      "text": "And Araba as far as the sea of Chenereth eastward, and as far as the sea of Araba; the salt sea eastward by the way to Asimoth, from Thaeman under Asedoth Phasga.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.4",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:4",
      "text": "And Og king of Basan, who dwelt in Astaroth and in Edrain, was left of the giants",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.5",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:5",
      "text": "ruling from mount Aermon and from Secchai, and over all the land of Basan to the borders of Gergesi, and Machi, and the half of Galaad of the borders of Seon king of Esebon.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.6",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:6",
      "text": "Moses the servant of the Lord and the children of Israel smote them; and Moses gave them by way of inheritance to Ruben, and Gad, and to the half tribe of Manasse.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.7",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:7",
      "text": "And these are the kings of the Amorites, whom Joshua and the children of Israel slew beyond Jordan by the sea of Balagad in the plain of Libanus, and as far as the mountain of Chelcha, as men go up to Seir: and Joshua gave it to the tribes of Israel to inherit according to their portion;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.8",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:8",
      "text": "in the mountain, and in the plain, and in Araba, and in Asedoth, and in the wilderness, and Nageb; the Chettite, and the Amorite, and the Chananite, and the Pherezite, and the Evite, and the Jebusite.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.9",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:9",
      "text": "The king of Jericho, and the king of Gai, which is near Baethel;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.10",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:10",
      "text": "the king of Jerusalem, the king of Chebron,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.11",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "joshua",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Joshua 12:11",
      "text": "the king of Jerimuth, the king of Lachis;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:joshua.12.12",
